## 2026-05-29 19:55 WIB — Section 1: Ingestion pipeline DONE

- **feat(brain)**: `AddDrawerFull(ctx, AddDrawerOpts)` di `internal/brain/write.go` — sibling `AddDrawer`, full param control (source_type, source_file, importance, chunk_index, mem_type, normalize_version, wing, room). Dedupe content_hash + sync ke `memory_fts` sama kaya AddDrawer. AddDrawer existing tetap untuk stub `/run`.
- **feat(ingest)**: package baru `internal/ingest/` — orchestrator `Submit()` + `SubmitBatch()` (anti short-circuit on error). `Sanitize()` normalize line ending + strip control char + collapse whitespace. `Score()` heuristic 0-10 (signal words, source reputation, length). Quality gate `minContentChars=20`.
- **feat(handlers)**: `handlers_brain_ingest.go` — `POST /api/brain/ingest/submit` (single) + `POST /api/brain/ingest/batch` (max 1000 items). Helper `ensureBrainReady()`. Existing `/run` stub tidak di-modify.
- **fix(build)**: `referensifile/go.mod` separate module — cegah `go build ./...` parent scan 101 .go reference file dengan external imports (same fix as Agent repo).
- **verified end-to-end** dengan 3 test:
  - submit single → drawer_id `df94ac62fc1679fd`, `added: true`
  - resubmit same content → `added: false` (dedupe kerja)
  - batch 3 items → `{total:3, added:1, deduped:1, skipped:1, failed:0}` (1 dup, 1 short, 1 valid)
  - Importance heuristic verified: default-scored `5.0` (manual+length boost), caller override `7.0` passed through.

### NOT included (defer ke section berikutnya per scope):
- Embedding generation (Section 5 — Embed worker)
- Re-score job berkala (Section 2 — Importance scorer refine)
- Backpressure rate-limit per source (Section 1 nice-to-have, ditunda sampai ada use case real)
- Doc-specific chunking strategy (ingest_docs.go) — saat ini caller harus chunk sendiri lalu pakai batch endpoint. Helper chunker ditunda sampai ada importer real.

